        <div class="main review-item" id="1134914">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cristine_guo/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1087648-7.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cristine_guo/" class="name">cristine</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2007-03-17" class="main-meta">2007-03-17 15:13:33</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1134914/">苏童：一首华丽忧伤的宫廷婉约词</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1134914_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1134914">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        读苏童，是适合在一个阴雨的天气中的。这氛围正契合了他的文字。苏童的文字是水做的，柔而媚。我想，读他的小说是应该关掉灯，点一枚蜡烛，和着摇曳而暧昧的烛火。他的文字刻着抹不掉的江南梅雨的气质，潮湿而阴冷。如果问我他的文字是什么颜色的，我要说应该是蓝色和黑色相见...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1134914-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1134914_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1134914_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1134914" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-1134914">
                                139
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="1134914" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-1134914">
                                4
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1134914/#comments" class="reply ">18回应</a>

                    <a href="javascript:;;" class="fold hidden">收起</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

            
    
    <div data-cid="3470861">
        <div class="main review-item" id="3470861">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4538051/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u4538051-1.jpg">
        </a>

